yingyinNormal.en: Well, clearly, that vital piece of information is going to win us the war.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很明显那条最重要的信息会帮助我们赢得战争。

yingyinNormal.en: Sacks gave us our injections. Your father made sure our vital signs were strong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 萨克斯给我们注射了药剂，你的父亲则负责我们的生命体征正常。

yingyinNormal.en: It all acts as a miniature pump, sucking in and concentrating vital carbon dioxide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们像小型的气泵，可将植物赖以生存的二氧化碳吸进植物体内并聚积起来。

yingyinNormal.en: You see those readouts? We can monitor your vital signs from anywhere on the planet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看到那些参数了吗？无论在哪我们都能监测到你的信号。

yingyinNormal.en: Tell them to quit treating your business like it's expendable and start treating it for what it is: vital to America's success.
yingyinNormal.zh: 告诉这些议员，别不把你们的企业不当回事儿，你们的企业对美国的进步至关重要，告诉他们认真对待。

yingyinNormal.en: Your planet is just now entering its genetic age. You understand very little about something which is a vital part of our reality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的星球刚刚进入它的基因时代。你们对宇宙万物的物质起源的了解少的可怜。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, this could disrupt highway and river traffic, but more importantly, could give them the opportunity to destroy vital dams in the region.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可能影响公路和河道交通，但更重要的是这会使他们有机会破坏该地区重要水坝。

yingyinNormal.en: But it's true. We put all your vital information into this dating site, answered all their questions just like you would, and they found a match for you. Her name is Amy Farrah Fowler.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但这是真的，我们把你所有重要信息上传到了交友网站，学着你的方式回答了他们所有问题，他们找到了个跟你匹配的，她叫艾米·菲拉·福勒。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, you're all valued employees. But as we undergo this transition to LIFE online we wanted to be candid with you that some of you will be determined non-vital employees to the new partnership.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，你们都是很有能力的员工。但是，当我们在将周刊网路化的过渡期间，我们要向你们坦白的说。
